  "title": "Staff Nurse @ HOME (North/ North-East) - No Overnight shift",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide preventive and curative medical services under the direction of the doctor and head nurse.</li>\n  <li>Monitor residents' overall health and oversee medical and nursing care routines.</li>\n  <li>Supervise and evaluate the performance of nursing aides and health attendants.</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing emergency situations within the Home.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Registered SN under SNB.</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of nursing experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
